{"tid":1816083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【捷克踢爆支那】捷克首富出錢宣傳中國","createTime":"2020-01-08T04:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T04:23:56.000Z","uid":289191,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9fcf7526e0441a802caf045b8a74d658c639138a","tid":1816083,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zpravy.aktualne.cz/domaci/home-credit-ppf-petr-kellner-campaign-china/r~265579361bf511ea926e0cc47ab5f122/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzpravy.aktualne.cz%2Fdomaci%2Fhome-credit-ppf-petr-kellner-campaign-china%2Fr~265579361bf511ea926e0cc47ab5f122%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IpS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=396a2187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zpravy.aktualne.cz/domaci/home-credit-ppf-petr-kellner-campaign-china/r~265579361bf511ea926e0cc47ab5f122/</a><br />\n篇文好長，重點包括：<br />\n1. 支那批准捷克銀行HOME CREDIT在支那做捷克貨幣業務。<br />\n2. HOME CREDIT搵公關公司C&amp;B在捷克宣傳中國。<br />\n3. 記者得到C&amp;B 向 HOME CREDIT claim 錢的 invoice。<br />\n4. 張 invoice 列出共二千 man-hours 的工作項目。<br />\n5. HOME CREDIT 和 C&amp;B 資助一間中國問題研究中心 Sinoskop。<br />\n6. Sinoskop 主力是對抗Charles University長期反中的 Sinopsis 研究中心。<br />\n7. C&amp;B 用錢安排 Sinoskop 的主任上捷克媒體接受訪問，甚至出手準備訪問問題。<br />\n8. C&amp;B 又用錢約稿唱好中國，放文章在捷克印刷傳媒和Sinoskop網站。被約稿者包括駐華學者，大使，及駐港總領事。<br />\n9. 支那關係成為捷克政壇鬥爭議題，總統親支，反對派以此攻擊政府。"},{"pid":"052dbcb8f631ff2b8635babe6d5f34430aa4db65","tid":1816083,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00ed25b9ee25cac24fd18a0a1743e0190572c16","tid":1816083,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37a21a2e0655e338ce4f7a6afe90a5232a2d1ac","tid":1816083,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:13:14.000Z","msg":"前排先去完布拉格，發現好多亞裔捷克人 會否係因為咁"},{"pid":"a39555e79f2a39b162bc38189a025e9ce776a00f","tid":1816083,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"全球反支<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c707d147415e3d964ad443c41642e6e2b39fdc","tid":1816083,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"捷克好反共，波蘭都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ad39ca0060006774d6043a96696f3a36b970ee","tid":1816083,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"有反中情緒 大陸就會落用錢搞果度<br />\n其實可以SET TRAP等大陸狗自己跳落去<br />\n或者何志平果段時間之前  已經有晒共識"},{"pid":"50ae7484ff2fe0d2d1cf2e190812ea7ac70ea47e","tid":1816083,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}